faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛去支那，啲人無回鄉証既話，咪又係入唔到境，咁咪又係有人屌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以旅遊都帶定啲美金防身會好啲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎Visa / master card 應該都買到野食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再唔係開海外提款拎錢都得啦"},{"pid":"2e0bd5f4fb8f53cea8db5d20e0cdac7a719df820","tid":377250,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>附近咁多機場唔揀越南？有限制？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當你澳門/珠海/深圳都受風，白雲應該得吓話</blockquote><br />\n深圳同廣州唔係隔咁遠<br />\n最近都要廈門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7d8ea37dadd34d0be21dc4a7015637752a38fa","tid":377250,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>附近咁多機場唔揀越南？有限制？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當你澳門/珠海/深圳都受風，白雲應該得吓話</blockquote><br />\n深圳同廣州唔係隔咁遠<br />\n最近都要廈門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔離post好似講過白雲唔肯收<br />\n除非架機要緊急降落<br />\n<br />\n所以通常台北，有啲廈門<br />\nDelta AA 嗰啲可能會揀日本或者泡菜"},{"pid":"3df08ba4de0c9db1b4400d568fc29ea65ee63a7e","tid":377250,"uid":6604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T04:03:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>明知越南要VISA 都飛班客去 有無腦架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉飛邊個場都唔比班客出去架啦<br />\n<br />\n其他公司隊轉飛台北啦<br />\n如果有d 客係支那出世又未去過台灣點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛去支那，啲人無回鄉証既話，咪又係入唔到境，咁咪又係有人屌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以旅遊都帶定啲美金防身會好啲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎Visa / master card 應該都買到野食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再唔係開海外提款拎錢都得啦</blockquote><br /